      "author_association" : "MEMBER",
      "body" : "Ideally the fuzzers would run on all branches, it is just that my personal efforts are focussed on the master branch. While the fuzzers should run on older branches, I won't be working on this actively myself.\r\n\r\nAbout the changes: The changes here won't disable the fuzzers when built locally or run in CI locally. If the goal is to disable the fuzz task in our Cirrus CI, it might be better to just do that in the cirrus.yml and not by putting CI-specific symbols (`CIRRUS_*`) in our CI-agnostic scripts (`./ci`).",
